value:
They agree to meet at the fountain.
But it appears only one shows up...

It's like they're on parallel paths.
How long until they find each other?

The water stops and they lock eyes!
They blush with embarrassment.

The fountain mesmerizes them both...
A lovely sight thanks to the confusion.
